    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Construction of non-trivial relativistic quantum fields in arbitrary space-time dimension via superposition of free fields
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Grothaus%2C+M">Martin Grothaus</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Nonnenmacher%2C+A">Andreas Nonnenmacher</a>
      
