    <p class="comments is-size-7">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Comments:</span>
      <span class="has-text-grey-dark mathjax">The proof of the cluster property (E4) for the superposition is wrong. Yoh Tanimoto and Wojciech Dybalski gave a counterexample s.t. the statement of cluster property can&#39;t hold in its full generality</span>
