        Acousto-electric Inverse Source Problem
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Li%2C+W">Wei Li</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Schotland%2C+J+C">John C. Schotland</a>, 
      
