    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Non-integrability of the Kepler and the two-body problem on the Heisenberg group
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Maciejewski%2C+A+J">Andrzej J. Maciejewski</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Stachowiak%2C+T">Tomasz Stachowiak</a>
      
