        <span>&nbsp;[<a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2103.10405">pdf</a>, <a href="https://arxiv.org/ps/2103.10405">ps</a>, <a href="https://arxiv.org/format/2103.10405">other</a>]&nbsp;</span>
