    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        The rational Sklyanin algebra and the Wilson and para-Racah polynomials
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Bergeron%2C+G">Geoffroy Bergeron</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Gaboriaud%2C+J">Julien Gaboriaud</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Vinet%2C+L">Luc Vinet</a>, 
      
