    <p class="abstract mathjax">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Abstract</span>:
      <span class="abstract-short has-text-grey-dark mathjax" id="2103.08906v1-abstract-short" style="display: inline;">
        For the Coulomb four-body problem, we show that there are finitely many isometry classes of planar central configurations (i.e., relative equilibria).
        
      </span>
      <span class="abstract-full has-text-grey-dark mathjax" id="2103.08906v1-abstract-full" style="display: none;">
        For the Coulomb four-body problem, we show that there are finitely many isometry classes of planar central configurations (i.e., relative equilibria).
