    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Iterated integrals over letters induced by quadratic forms
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Ablinger%2C+J">J. Ablinger</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Bl%C3%BCmlein%2C+J">J. Blümlein</a>, 
      
