    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Eddy heat exchange at the boundary under white noise turbulence
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Flandoli%2C+F">Franco Flandoli</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Galeati%2C+L">Lucio Galeati</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Luo%2C+D">Dejun Luo</a>
      
