    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Around quantum ergodicity
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Dyatlov%2C+S">Semyon Dyatlov</a>
      
    </p>
    
    <p class="abstract mathjax">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Abstract</span>:
      <span class="abstract-short has-text-grey-dark mathjax" id="2103.08093v1-abstract-short" style="display: inline;">
        We discuss Shnirelman&#39;s Quantum Ergodicity Theorem, giving an outline of a proof and an overview of some of the recent developments in mathematical Quantum Chaos.
        
      </span>
      <span class="abstract-full has-text-grey-dark mathjax" id="2103.08093v1-abstract-full" style="display: none;">
        We discuss Shnirelman&#39;s Quantum Ergodicity Theorem, giving an outline of a proof and an overview of some of the recent developments in mathematical Quantum Chaos.
        <a class="is-size-7" style="white-space: nowrap;" onclick="document.getElementById('2103.08093v1-abstract-full').style.display = 'none'; document.getElementById('2103.08093v1-abstract-short').style.display = 'inline';">&#9651; Less</a>
      </span>
    </p>
    

    <p class="is-size-7"><span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Submitted</span> 14 March, 2021; 
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">originally announced</span> March 2021.
      
    </p>
    
    <p class="comments is-size-7">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Comments:</span>
      <span class="has-text-grey-dark mathjax">18 pages, 3 figures; submitted to the special issue of Annales Mathématiques du Québec in honor of Alexander Shnirelman&#39;s 75th birthday</span>
    </p>
    

    

    
  </li>

  <li class="arxiv-result">
    <div class="is-marginless">
      <p class="list-title is-inline-block"><a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2103.08037">arXiv:2103.08037</a>
        <span>&nbsp;[<a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2103.08037">pdf</a>, <a href="https://arxiv.org/ps/2103.08037">ps</a>, <a href="https://arxiv.org/format/2103.08037">other</a>]&nbsp;</span>
      </p>
      <div class="tags is-inline-block">
        <span class="tag is-small is-link tooltip is-tooltip-top" data-tooltip="High Energy Physics - Theory">hep-th</span>
        
          
            <span class="tag is-small is-grey tooltip is-tooltip-top" data-tooltip="General Relativity and Quantum Cosmology">gr-qc</span>
          
